	<text>
		<body>
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002040_0001"><!--pb/@n='71r'--></pb>
<lb/><p rend="center"><placeName><settlement type="town">Hamilton</settlement></placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="1" unit="words"/><date when="1864-08-06">6 August</date></p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="7" unit="chars"/><date>1864</date></p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear <persName>Waller</persName></p>
<lb/><p><space extent="3" unit="chars"/>I wrote you
<lb/>a "Young man
<lb/>about town"ish
<lb/>letter yesterday
<lb/>This is business
<lb/>Be good enough
<lb/>to send the enclosed
<lb/>to <persName>Meller</persName> at your
<lb/>earliest convenience
                
    

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002040_0002"><!--pb/@n='71v'--></pb>
<lb/>I want him to get
<lb/>through his brother
<lb/>a collage for me
<lb/>near <placeName><settlement type="city">London</settlement></placeName>
<lb/>where I may be
<lb/>retired from
<lb/>everyone <persName><choice><abbr>HW</abbr><expan>Horace Waller</expan></choice></persName>
<lb/>included.</p>
<lb/><p>I am still with
<lb/>my mother &amp;
<lb/>family and hope
<lb/>you are enjoying
<lb/>yourself - Between
<lb/>ourselves <persName>Bishop

    

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002040_0003"><!--pb/@n='72r'--></pb>
<lb/>Tozer</persName>'s conduct
<lb/>has staggered his
<lb/>friends and 
<lb/>having been
<lb/>consulted I have
<lb/>given my
<lb/>opinion of it
<lb/>pretty plainly
<lb/>but I hope
<lb/>without malice
<lb/>He is pretending
<lb/>that at <placeName><region>Zanzibar</region></placeName>
<lb/>he will work
<lb/>in <placeName><region>Central Africa</region></placeName>
<lb/>"The merchants

    

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002040_0004"><!--pb/@n='72v'--></pb>
<lb/>of that great Emporium
<lb/>underselling others
<lb/>even at <persName><settlement type="village">Tette</settlement></persName>"
<lb/>I say <placeName><region>Central Africa</region></placeName>
<lb/>is abandoned
<lb/>but they will get
<lb/>nice little comforts
<lb/>&amp; luxuries at
<lb/><placeName><region>Zanzibar</region></placeName></p>
<lb/><p><choice><abbr>DL.</abbr><expan>David Livingstone</expan></choice></p>
			
</div>
